Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Grenada press ban lifted
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xbns
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 6 Nov 1983
Press begins to uncover the fuller, and more complex, story of the Grenada invasion. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.